      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FARMOR SENIOR (3) ran below best last time finishing seventh (24.66) over 407m at this track from Box 3. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has ability and can bounce back. FLYING BLOSSOM (7) has mixed form recently, finishing eighth (22.64) in a P5 at Townsville latest but did run well two back when in the frame. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. SUMMER'S EDITION (5) was always prominent from this same draw last time and boxed on well to place (22.01) in a OPEN over 390m at Q Lakeside. Leading player again. MR. UNFLAPPABLE (6) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a one length second (23.76) in a Grade 5 at this track.",
